metadata.name: Celestial Odyssey
metadata.description:
4K | 4096 * 2160 px | MPEG-4 | 25 MB

Designed and developed in Photoshop and After Effects.

---



Across the celestial canvas, we soar, a journey through the heavens, forevermore.
Stars twinkle like diamonds in the cosmic sea, guiding our odyssey, setting our spirits free.

Galaxies swirl and nebulas dance, in hues of cosmic beauty, we take a chance.
Astronauts traverse the realms above, bathing in the radiance of the celestial love.

Through time-lapsed frames, we witness the sublime, celestial wonders, frozen in time.
Auroras paint the sky with vibrant light, illuminating the darkness, a celestial delight.
